10. what happens after db pod deletion?
Observation-
After DB pod deletion Shocket connetion of Result and Worker pod get down.
To restablish Shocket connetion again with db pod, Result and Worker pod get restarted.


[root@ip-172-31-32-161 ~]# kubectl get po
NAME                      READY   STATUS    RESTARTS   AGE
db-b54cd94f4-h4brp        1/1     Running   0          22m
redis-868d64d78-6sc8w     1/1     Running   0          96m
result-5d57b59f4b-tqkxt   1/1     Running   1          96m
vote-94849dc97-5mnms      1/1     Running   0          92m
worker-dd46d7584-vhxq2    1/1     Running   1          51m

12. What you did in order to make the result pod work.

There is no manual intervention for result pod to work again. It get Restarted to restablish connection again with new DB pod (Only when new DB pod come in 1/1 running state)
